//Installing Docker on Ubuntu machine .
--------------
Log in to the any available linux machine & execute the following

curl -sSL https://get.docker.com/ | sh
sudo service docker start
sudo usermod -aG docker $(id -un)
----------------

Checking installation

Once you have finished installation on any of the above mentioned Operating Systems apart from Windows7,
open the terminal (Powershell for Windows) and execute the following commands
********
docker version
docker info
********
